These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, june, april, july, november, december, may
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, chinese, mexican, nigerian, thai
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the chinese##1
 2. the mexican is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the canadian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is in the middle##1
 6. the argentine is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is the argentine##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the australian##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Birthday           | november | july | june | april | february | december | may |
| Nationality   | argentine    | mexican   | chinese      | nigerian | canadian    | australian    | thai         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
City: boston, prague, edinburgh, new-york, marseilles, san-francisco, hamburg
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, funk, gospel, pop, punk, rock, soul
 1. the fan of punk is the person traveling to new-york##1
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 3. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
 4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 5. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the fan of punk is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| City          | boston | prague | marseilles | new-york | san-francisco | hamburg | edinburgh |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | gospel   | pop   | punk      | d&b       | soul       | rock     |

