.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, brazilian, indonesian, australian, russian, german, colombian
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, freelancer, mechanic, photographer, scientist, teacher, writer
 1. the brazilian is on the left of the russian##1
 2. the russian is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the freelancer is on the left of the colombian##1
 4. the indian is on the right of the german##1
 5. the bartender is the russian##1
 6. the mechanic is on the right of the freelancer##1
 7. the freelancer is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the photographer##1
 9. the german is the photographer##1
10. the indonesian is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the photographer is in the middle##1
12. the colombian is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | russian     | indonesian  | german       | indian       | colombian  | australian   |
| Job    | teacher  | bartender | writer | photographer | freelancer | mechanic | scientist |

