.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary, disaster, thriller, romance, crime, horror
7 different pets are kept: dog, fish, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig, horse, snake
 1. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | disaster | crime     | thriller | horror | romance | martial-arts |
| Pet     | snake   | frog    | guinea-pig | horse     | dog         | goldfish     | fish        |

