.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-8::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, vegafina, baccarat, pall-mall, tiparillo, swisher, montecristo
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, taxi, train
 1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 2. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
 3. the vegafina-smoker is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 6. the baccarat-smoker is the person driving the roller##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person driving the boat is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 9. the swisher-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Cigar       | vegafina   | pall-mall | montecristo | swisher | dannemann     | baccarat | tiparillo |
| Transport   | quad-bike | taxi      | boat        | train         | helicopter | roller     | scooter |

