.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-9::.
There 7 different types of food: broccoli, corn, grapes, kiwi, papaya, radish, watermelon
7 different pets are kept: ferret, rat, mouse, snake, turtle, dog, goat
 1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1
 5. the owner of the snake is the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is the person eating radish##1
 7. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating corn##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
11. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
| Food        | corn | broccoli | grapes | kiwi     | radish | watermelon | papaya |
| Pet   | dog | snake  | goat    | ferret | turtle | rat       | mouse   |

