.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-11::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, lemonade, soy-milk, fanta, 7up, almond-milk
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, french, german, italian, japanese, spanish, thai
 1. the argentine is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the spanish##1
 4. the french is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the italian is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the french is in the middle##1
10. the french is on the right of the german##1
11. the italian is on the left of the japanese##1
12. the thai is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |   4    |     5     |    6    |   7    |
| Beverage          | fanta | juice     | 7up | lemonade | cola      | almond-milk  | soy-milk |
| Nationality   | italian   | japanese | german  | french | argentine | spanish | thai   |

