.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-12::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola, milk, mirinda, sprite, tea
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, orange, light-blue, white, emerald, brown, turquise
1. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
5. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
6. the person who likes turquise is the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person who likes emerald is in the middle##1
8. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
9. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4     |    5    |     6     |      7      |
| Beverage      | tea       | milk    | sprite    | 7up       | cola    | mirinda   | almond-milk |
| Color   | light-blue | brown | blood-red | emerald | orange | white | turquise        |

