.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-13::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, chess, fishing, gardening, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
7 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, ferret, hamster, mouse, fish, chinchilla
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 6. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 8. the owner of the mouse is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | chess   | singing | baking | puzzles | gardening | fishing  |
| Pet   | hamster  | mouse | chinchilla  | ferret | fish | frog     | guinea-pig |

